Package moblima.model

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
moblima.model.Booking
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Booking extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a booking made for a ticket. Linked to a Ticket booked by a particular Moviegoer.
